      <akn:section eId="sec_47_398_01">
        <akn:num>47-398.01</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Permitting designated authority to borrow funds for preconstruction activities relating to Gallery Place sports arena.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-398_01_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Permitting borrowing. —</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-398_01_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Treatment of debt created. — Any debt created pursuant to subsection (a) of this section shall not:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_47-398_01_c">
      <akn:num>(c)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Designated authority defined. — The term “designated authority” means the Redevelopment Land Agency or such other District of Columbia government agency or instrumentality designated by the Mayor of the District of Columbia for purposes of carrying out any Arena preconstruction activities.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
